### Configuration & Environment

- Central settings: [settings.py](mdc:src/ultimate_discord_intelligence_bot/settings.py)
- Feature flags: `ENABLE_<AREA>_<FEATURE>`
- Document env changes: [docs/configuration.md](mdc:docs/configuration.md)
- Validate startup configuration using existing validation utilities and fail fast.

### Environment Variables

- Prefer explicit, required variables; provide safe defaults only where appropriate.
- Keep secrets out of code. Use environment or secret managers.
- Ensure tenant-aware values are namespaced by `(tenant, workspace)`.

### Patterns

- Read configuration once, inject into components; avoid ad-hoc `os.getenv` calls deep in code.
- Use typed accessors and validation; raise clear errors with remediation hints.
